n-top:0.6em;'></div></div> 4 an armour of the hip or the loins. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>deśaḥ</span> the loins. (<div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>ṭi</span> or <span class='sdata'>ṭī</span>) <span class='sdata'>prothaḥ</span> the buttocks. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>mālikā</span> a woman's zone or girdle. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>rohakaḥ</span> the rider of an elephant (who sits upon the hinder parts of the elephant as distinct from the driver). <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>śīrṣakaḥ</span> the loins. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>śṛṃkhalā</span> a girdle furnished with small bells. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>sūtraṃ</span> a zone or waistband.","evidence":{"band":4,"band_label":"attested -- look up","rank_all":47379,"count_all":1,"first_era":"1700","genre":null,"example":{"sa":"kaṭī","ru":"зады","work":"05_ramayana-sundarakanda","passage":"9.61","kind":"translation","source":"corpus_lexicon.jsonl (pwg_ru Phase 4, SanskritLexicography/RussianTranslation)"},"badges":[{"field":"band","value":4,"label":"attested -- look up","source":"kosha frequency layer, rank_all (DCS archive.sqlite M9 via VisualDCS)"},{"field":"count_all","value":1,"label":"1 attestations in DCS","source":"DCS archive.sqlite M9 (VisualDCS)"},{"field":"first_era","value":"1700","label":"first attested: 1700","source":"DCS archive.sqlite M9 (VisualDCS)"},{"field":"genre","value":null,"label":"genre sketch not derivable from current DCS extraction (only a chronological period vector is stored, no per-genre breakdown)","source":"n/a -- gap documented, not fabricated (see app/evidence.py)"}]}}]}